{"tid":1867542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來HKTV市值已經迫近CCTVB......","createTime":"2020-02-07T08:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T13:56:44.000Z","uid":228995,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdb8de065a3b6951e2944d3c33723750bd96fcc","tid":1867542,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n武漢肺炎情況持續，港股今日由低位回升，恆指今日升超過 706 點 ，香港電視的股價炒上近七個月高位，今日單日升近 9 % 至 5.2 元。累計香港電視過去一個月急升約五成，市值漲至 42.68 億，市值進一步追近 TVB。<br />\n<br />\n口罩供應仍然緊張，香港電視今日發帖講述在東南亞國家尋找口罩供應的過程，又指已確認日後的供應量，但因為部分因素未能確認，暫時未能預告返貨量，獲網民大量好評，「但只要我哋一有消息，一定會通知大家！敬請大家請耐心等候 。」<br />\n<br />\n香港電視當日未能成功申請免費電視牌照，在主席王維基之後轉戰網購，至今日市值達 42.68 億元，追近當日反對港視發牌 TVB（電視廣播，511）。以往市值達數百億的 TVB 因業績，今日收市市值為 52.91 億元。<br />\n<br />\nTVB 前年購入星美（198）新發行、本金總額逾 8 億元的可換股貸款及債券，因星美財困，連累 TVB 需撇賬 5 億元。業績欠佳，加上投資失利，過去一年股價跌約兩成。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後TVB係咪要將TVBbuddy放上HKTVmall 散貨"},{"pid":"6740dfc99108481312071eca2ed7abf8d976caf9","tid":1867542,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"誠哥，維基，香港之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCctxb弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65b10e9f4f2dc237d10412a385f0efd03ae712b","tid":1867542,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9cb95be1278ae410dad033c9bce15d6d68b2a0","tid":1867542,"uid":205462,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"Cctvb嘅高層用好多前ccatv, 前畸寶tv嘅智將，視𡃤共為己任，幕前亦都一樣，自己培育嘅偽人，就百般武藝樣樣唔得，咁點會唔死?"},{"pid":"ee70123771b052ea6bef1fb17e0dbd63ce514095","tid":1867542,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"遲D收購TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92398e0e48bce16a789b841cb10e377bff6bcd0f","tid":1867542,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59516181e15c7cda604869d24b97e05795e1dd4a","tid":1867542,"uid":107577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於輸<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af4f60915969bad21a7a5d9d47ca322c8a2e238c","tid":1867542,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"香港人繼續支持HKTVMALL"},{"pid":"ce7fcb0dd6c5dac18be1e2467e39e11c4ef01380","tid":1867542,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee70123771b052ea6bef1fb17e0dbd63ce514095","tid":1867542,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"遲D收購TVB<img